{
  "stem": "5795.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He looked at me and said, I'm-- I'm-- I'm-- I'm sorry to upset the reverend gentleman.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I still say we've got to dump the Jews of Poland on the shores of Palestine before it's too late-- Polish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This was 1938.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In 1945, for my sins, I went into Belsen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And one of the young men I met there, after I came to-- my senses were numbed, at least for minutes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then I start to hear Jabotinsky's voice-- and his advice, and his appeal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then this-- then I start to talk to myself, apparently.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's very difficult to describe what-- what I went through mentally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He came to us, in 1936.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he said, don't learn the value of silks and satins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Learn the value of a gun-- how to defend yourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And get out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We ignored him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Many people considered him as a fascist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Many people-- the leaders-- consider him a troublemaker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow-- so then-- then I was-- where I'm going to?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going back into-- into Belsen now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then-- then we started-- then we started working, talking to people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had nothing except my own hands and a-- and a mouth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, so when-- so-- so naturally, when war broke out-- just before war broke out, many people volunteered.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a lot of the young men of my community also volunteered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, I got that in 1940-- '41.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the funniest thing was when I was gonna go there to receive it, you know, in my cap and gown, and-- and the certificate, the order was it had to be canceled.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
